item.numina.component_parachute.desc: Baaq fudud oo dib loo isticmaali karo oo la dejin karo lagana soo kabsan karo midair.
tooltip.numina.charging_base: Charges alaabta ay alaabtiisa qalabaysan tahay
item.numina.component_ion_thruster.desc: aasaas ahaan waa xawaare yar oo qoyaan yar. Waxay dardar gelisaa ions ilaa xawaaraha ku dhow iftiinka si ay u soo saaraan durkinta.
item.numina.component_laser_emitter.desc: A multicolored laser array which cheaply bedeli kartaa muuqaalka wax.
item.numina.battery_elite.desc: Isdhexgalka batteriga ugu horumarsan si aad u kaydiso tiro ballaaran oo tamar ah.
item.numina.component_glider_wing.desc: baal aerodynamic fudud oo leh electromagnet ah si degdeg ah gaynta iyo dib u laabashada.
item.numina.component_magnet.desc: A qalab macdan ah abuura beerta magnetic kaas oo alaabta jiido dhinaca ciyaaryahanka.
tooltip.numina.changeModes: hababka isbeddelka: Riix oo xaji tirada hotbar booska ku hotbar ku Power Fist ku jiro.
item.numina.battery_ultimate.desc: tijaabo qalab kaydinta awood dhamaadka sare, hadda la ku dhowaad lahayn fursad ay qarxaan (waxaan u maleynayaa). Inkastoo ay jiraan warar aad u xun, kuma salaysna tiknoolajiyada ajnabiga ah ee la xaday.
item.numina.component_servo.desc: Nooc gaar ah oo motor ah oo isticmaalaya signal garaaca wadnaha modulated si ay u dejiyaan dhaqdhaqaaqyo aad u sax ah.
tooltip.numina.pressShift: Press wareejin wixii macluumaad dheeraad ah.
item.numina.battery_advanced.desc: Isku-duwidda batteriga si loogu ogolaado sheyga si uu u keydiyo tamarta.
item.numina.component_carbon_myofiber.de: Xidhmo yar oo ah fiber-ka carbonka, oo loo safeeyey si loogu isticmaalo muruqyada macmaliga ah.
tooltip.numina.noModules: No modules rakibay! Tani waa wax aan waxtar lahayn ilaa aad ku darto qaar ka mid ah modules at Shaxda Tinker a.
item.numina.component_wiring.desc: Nooca A gaarka ah ee fiilooyinka leh awood koronto sare iyo sax, lagama maarmaan u ah elektarooniga xasaasi ah ee hubka awoodda.
rakibtay module galay item qaybsan doortay halka ciyaaryahan waa in hab hal abuur leh
item.numina.component_myofiber_gel.desc: Jinka A qaro weyn, jinka dardargelinta, oo kufiican u dhexeeya myofibers ee muruqa macmal ah.
Koronto, murqo macmal ah, oo leh dhaqdhaqaaqyo yar marka loo eego murqaha aadanaha laakiin amarrada xajmiga ayaa xoog badan leh.
item.numina.component_control_circuit.de: A microcontroller fudud networkable isku dubaridka qayb shaqsi ah.
item.numina.component_solar_panel.desc: Qalab xasaasi ah oo fudud oo korontada ka dhalinaya qorraxda.
item.numina.battery_basic.desc: Integre una batería para permitir que el artículo almacene energía.
item.numina.component_rubber_hose.desc: tuubo caag oo si xoogan loo qallafsan yahay oo awood u leh kulaylka ba'an ama qabow
item.numina.component_computer_chip.desc: Wareegtada kontoroolka oo la casriyeeyay oo ay ku jiraan processor kaas oo awood u leh xisaabinta horumarsan.
item.numina.component_solenoid.desc: Wires nabar agagaarka a core ferromagnetic soo saara electromagnet aasaasiga ah.
item.numina.component_field_emitter.desc: qalab advanced kaas oo si toos ah u maareeya beeraha electromagnetic iyo gravitational ee meel.
